title: Esim not working with Google FI on Pixel 3 XL
content:
Hi guys,

Does anybody knows if there is a known issue with the eSIM on Pixel 3 XL running Android Q beta? 

I can't seem to be able to activate my eSIM (I am.using Fi) and was wondering if that was a software issue before I try to reinstall Pie.

Thanks!
